author: stefan2
msg: When modifying packed revprops, we may need to split the pack file to
stay within the configured file size limits.  After the split, on of
the pack files will start at a later revision than the manifest.
Splitting the same pack again will resulted in the file names being
picked from the wrong manifest entries.
(packed_revprops_t): store the revision of the first manifest entry
(repack_stream_open): fix the calculation of the manifest entry index
